《'''我的感覺'''》（{{lang-en|''Personal Feeling''}}）是香港歌手[[黎明|黎明]]的第四張粵語[[錄音室專輯|錄音室專輯]]<ref>{{Cite web|url = https://www.881903.com/highlight/2366988/%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E7%88%86%E8%B0%B7-%E6%98%8E%E6%97%A5%E4%B9%8B%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E6%AD%8C/11%E6%9C%8819%E6%97%A5%E4%B9%8B%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E6%AD%8C|title = 11月19日之廣東歌|date = 2020-11-18|publisher = 商業電台|language = zh|accessdate = 2021-06-07|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210607125357/https://www.881903.com/highlight/2366988/%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E7%88%86%E8%B0%B7-%E6%98%8E%E6%97%A5%E4%B9%8B%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E6%AD%8C/11%E6%9C%8819%E6%97%A5%E4%B9%8B%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E6%AD%8C|archive-date = 2021-06-07|dead-url = yes}}</ref>，全碟由[[陳永明_(音樂人)|陳永明]]監製，收錄了10首歌曲，於1991年11月19日由唱片公司[[寶麗金|寶麗金]]首次發行<ref>{{Cite book | author = 張錦華| title = 中國當代流行音樂的傳播與接受研究 | location = 北京 | publisher = 中國傳媒大學出版社 | date = 2016-03 | pages = 23 | ISBN = 9787565715181 |language = zh-hans}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book | author = 林玉鑫| title = 百歌爭嗚 成名曲、流行曲快樂大放送 | location = 北京 | publisher = 海潮出版社 | date = 2001-01 | pages = 371 | ISBN = 7801512839 |language = zh-hans}}</ref>，獲得四白金銷量<ref>{{Cite book|title = 黎天王錢來自有方|location =香港|publisher = 娛樂天下周刊 |date =1994|url = https://i.imgur.com/lvCUdMV.jpg |language =zh|accessdate =2022-01-30|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210501020407/https://i.imgur.com/lvCUdMV.jpg|archive-date =2021-05-01|dead-url =yes}}</ref>，其後於2018年以[[黑膠唱片|黑膠唱片]]形式重新發行<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.discogs.com/%E9%BB%8E%E6%98%8E-%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E6%84%9F%E8%A6%BA-Personal-Feeling/release/9196362 |title = 黎明–我的感覺|date = 2018 |publisher = Discogs |language = en|accessdate =2021-06-01|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200925011950/https://www.discogs.com/%E9%BB%8E%E6%98%8E-%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E6%84%9F%E8%A6%BA-Personal-Feeling/release/9196362|archive-date = 2020-09-25|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

==製作概念==
《我的感覺》專輯的同名歌曲〈我的感覺〉是黎明首次作曲的作品<ref>{{cite news|language = zh|url = https://hd.stheadline.com/life/hotpicks/20210713/600551/|title = 1991年連出三張唱片 仲有時間作曲 以「天濛光」筆名作《我的感覺》 成為Fans心目中金曲之一|publisher = 頭條日報|date = 2021-07-13|accessdate = 2022-01-23|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220123074423/https://i.imgur.com/OV5wJjY.jpg|archive-date = 2022-01-23|dead-url = no}}</ref>，將他自己對生活、工作、朋友、家庭、愛情的看法寫入歌曲中<ref>{{Cite book | author = 則夫 | title = 黎明 Cover Story | location = 香港 | publisher = Music Express雜誌 | date = 1991 | pages = 4|accessdate = 2020-09-25|url = https://wx4.sinaimg.cn/large/67df3b43ly1gi4mmxr89ej20u0140b2a.jpg|language = zh|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200925013422/https://wx4.sinaimg.cn/large/67df3b43ly1gi4mmxr89ej20u0140b2a.jpg|archive-date = 2020-09-25|dead-url = yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language = zh |title = 黎明譜曲我的感覺 寓情於歌訴及心聲 |publisher = 大公報 |pages = 20 |date = 1991-10-21}}</ref>，由[[盧東尼|盧東尼]]編曲，黎明表示「天濛光」的意思與「[[拂曉|黎明]]」相近，並寓意自己的音樂事業正處於開始階段，故以此為筆名<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://i.imgur.com/WCAwDOo.jpg|title =缺點要改正 事實要面對 從未想過靠胡混成功|year =1991|publisher =大眾電視|language =zh|accessdate =2021-08-07|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210806235912/https://i.imgur.com/WCAwDOo.jpg|archive-date = 2020-09-25|dead-url = yes}}</ref>，這首歌由[[向雪懷|向雪懷]]填詞，歌詞句子之間沒有一個完整的脈絡，以一段瀕臨中止的愛情為題材，通過歌詞表達出對愛情的失望及頗有[[存在主義|存在主義]]的對一切都不甚了了的感覺<ref>{{Cite book | author = 朱耀偉 | title = 香港粵語流行歌詞研究 七十年代中期至八十年代中期II | location = 香港 | publisher = 亮光文化有限公司 | date = 2016-03 | pages = 163－164 | ISBN = 9789888365296| language = zh}}</ref>。另一首主打歌曲〈今夜你會不會來〉由[[簡寧|簡寧]]填詞，歌詞內容由一些求愛訊息堆砌而成<ref name="朱米高">{{Cite web|url = https://michaelchu-73917.medium.com/patreon%E6%9C%83%E5%93%A1%E5%B0%88%E4%BA%AB-%E4%BB%8A%E6%99%9A%E4%BD%A0%E6%9C%83%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83%E4%BE%86-%E6%B1%82%E6%84%9B%E8%A8%8A%E6%81%AF%E4%BA%82%E6%A7%8D%E6%8E%83%E5%B0%84-3f872c4ee9af
|title =《今夜你會不會來》求愛訊息亂槍掃射|author = 朱米高|date = 2020-12-26|publisher = 千千闋歌與我常在|language = zh|accessdate = 2022-02-20|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210123235928/https://michaelchu-73917.medium.com/patreon%E6%9C%83%E5%93%A1%E5%B0%88%E4%BA%AB-%E4%BB%8A%E6%99%9A%E4%BD%A0%E6%9C%83%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83%E4%BE%86-%E6%B1%82%E6%84%9B%E8%A8%8A%E6%81%AF%E4%BA%82%E6%A7%8D%E6%8E%83%E5%B0%84-3f872c4ee9af
|archive-date = 2021-01-23|dead-url = no}}</ref>，這首歌其中一個版本的音樂短片由[[小美_(香港)|小美]]執導，黎明和[[李嘉欣|李嘉欣]]合作演出<ref>{{Cite book|title = 黎明 情緣待續|location = 香港|publisher = 100 marks magazine|date = 1991-11-02|accessdate = 2022-01-21|url = https://i.imgur.com/YLAnu4H.jpg|language = zh|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220121064419/https://i.imgur.com/YLAnu4H.jpg|archive-date = 2022-01-21|dead-url = yes}}</ref>。專輯的第9首歌曲由監製陳永明、填詞人小美及歌手黎明共同命名，黎明認為此歌曲的節奏、歌詞和氣氛溫馨活潑，曾經提議將歌曲命名為「月下的戇男」，惟遭到否決，眾人其後決定從歌詞中尋找合適的詞句，起初計劃以「造個夢找個心頭最愛」作為曲名，後來決定命名為〈邂逅、偶遇、散步、對望〉<ref>{{Cite book |title = 關於黎明「邂逅、偶遇、散步、對望」的故事 | location = 香港 | publisher = NO.1 雜誌 |date = 1991|url = https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/67df3b43ly1gi4mnc9kx6j20u01407wi.jpg|language = zh|accessdate = 2020-09-25|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200925013121/https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/67df3b43ly1gi4mnc9kx6j20u01407wi.jpg|archive-date = 2020-09-25|dead-url = yes}}</ref>。

